{"tid":889081,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Sulli雪莉緊身上衣響應No Bra　性感躺草地解放：冬天不要來","createTime":"2018-11-04T09:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T00:47:37.000Z","uid":58335,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d2ce258030fc0dcbf0dfdbb4229e09fd4d5dcaea","tid":889081,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:42:40.000Z","msg":"佢真係痴左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n韓國女藝人Sulli雪莉自從退出f(x)後就樂於做自己，不太介意別人的目光。經常都會上傳性感相、意識相到自己的Instagram喜和網友分享。而Sulli雪莉昨日（2日）又更新自己的Instagram又上傳了多張性感照，引起大家熱烈討論，有人認為她純粹博出位，亦有人指她其實是「Free the nipple」運動的支持者。<br />\n<br />\nSulli雪莉最近就通過節目《真理商店》和大家見面，在節目中Sulli雪莉都有穿上胸罩拍攝，但昨日更新的Instagram照片中，雪莉就再次大解放！她就發文表示自己不想冬天到來。雪莉在照片中坐於草地上，穿了緊身上衣，讓自己的身材完美地展示出，但最叫大家關注的就是雪莉沒有穿胸罩的圖片，儼如赤裸裸地露出胸部一樣。<br />\nFree the Nipple由電影變成平權運動<br />\n<br />\n一如以往地有不少網民都不滿雪莉的行為「令人民望」、「傷風敗俗」、「好像想要被關注」，另一方面就有網友支持雪莉表示「有必要讓女性從令人感到不便的胸罩中解放出來」、「讓No Bra感到羞愧的人是問題」、「雖然因爲不成熟而受到關注，但是很坦蕩」反應十分兩極。其實「Free the nipple」並非新鮮事，最早可以追溯至2014年在美國上映、由Lina Esco執導的同名電影《Free the Nipple》，電影講述一班年輕女性走上紐約街頭，用表演與塗鴉抗議關於女性胸部的法律和社會禁忌，隨後演變成為一場爭取性別平權的運動，試圖透過女性裸露上半身，呼籲大眾可以公平看待男性與女性裸露上半身的行為，強調身體的除罪化和去性化。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/254774/sulli%E9%9B%AA%E8%8E%89%E7%B7%8A%E8%BA%AB%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%A3%E9%9F%BF%E6%87%89no-bra-%E6%80%A7%E6%84%9F%E8%BA%BA%E8%8D%89%E5%9C%B0%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE-%E5%86%AC%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E4%BE%86?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=entertainment\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F254774%2Fsulli%25E9%259B%25AA%25E8%258E%2589%25E7%25B7%258A%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E9%259F%25BF%25E6%2587%2589no-bra-%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%2584%259F%25E8%25BA%25BA%25E8%258D%2589%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2594%25BE-%25E5%2586%25AC%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E4%25BE%2586%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dentertainment&d=wzQ11qHcU%2B4SXBjieBAQhP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=9b8a4190\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/254774/sulli%E9%9B%AA%E8%8E%89%E7%B7%8A%E8%BA%AB%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%A3%E9%9F%BF%E6%87%89no-bra-%E6%80%A7%E6%84%9F%E8%BA%BA%E8%8D%89%E5%9C%B0%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE-%E5%86%AC%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E4%BE%86?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=entertainment</a>"},{"pid":"045b3678149940944f4b7156d2169df5fd99f643","tid":889081,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a380a99e46c4dc995798093b17a28ffc50379f","tid":889081,"uid":3405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:51:16.000Z","msg":"癲雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fff69d570f6a361c9a7757ef1fb5b2e903edbbd","tid":889081,"uid":149435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:57:15.000Z","msg":"都唔係第一日嘅事"},{"pid":"feb772f95323442ed4864bf5fc2cee695b3e4a30","tid":889081,"uid":96,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:59:33.000Z","msg":"一如以往地有不少網民都不滿雪莉的行為「令人民望」、「傷風敗俗」、「好像想要被關注」<br />\n<br />\nKpop啲淫舞本身就傷風敗俗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d4c6f7ab58f7c03a088fcd127e8cb1dbddf334","tid":889081,"uid":56444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:59:37.000Z","msg":"Mo ball"},{"pid":"d1ada940f1098df934fb6b4ad96ffc5c302915ed","tid":889081,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:13:02.000Z","msg":"ho ball"},{"pid":"c05d0eaefa6e85952b9f4f35866f6bc561abb13c","tid":889081,"uid":133086,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:16:11.000Z","msg":"